* NOW HERE'S THE SUN,
IT'S ALL RIGHT *

50:33.660 --> 50:36.652
* NOW HERE'S THE MOON,
IT'S ALL RIGHT *

50:36.760 --> 50:39.320
* BUT EVERY TIME
YOU CLOSE YOUR EYES *

50:39.430 --> 50:43.491
* IT'S ALL RIGHT,
IT'S ALL RIGHT *

